Package: PKAEvis
Type: Package
Title: Visualize longitudinal adverse event data with pharmacokinetic profiles
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Kenta Yoshida
Maintainer: Kenta Yoshida <yoshida.kenta@gene.com>
Description: The PKAEvis package provide visualization tools to explore 
    relationships between adverse event (AE) occurance/duration and drug 
    exposures in individuals. Currently this package provide one functionality:
    to overlay duration of AE on the individual concentration-time profiles. 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports:
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    ggplot2 (>= 2.1),
    cowplot
License: MIT | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
